description:
&lt;p&gt;This is a fantastic opportunity to launch your Occupational Health Nursing career with no prior experience essential, and opportunities for training and development are available.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Occupational Health team is based at the Royal United Hospitals Bath main site and provides a range of services to both the public and private sectors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate will be innovative, confident, have excellent communication skills, proficient IT skills and a flexible pro-active approach to be able to manage a varied and demanding workload.&lt;/p&gt;
